lead_paragraph: Two goals from Alexis Sanchez and another from Theo Walcott ended Bournemouth's brave resistance at the Emirates stadium as Arsenal won 3-1 to stay in touch with the Premier League leaders on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Sanchez's Double for Arsenal Ends Brave Bournemouth's Hopes
